# MiniBolt Info

A bash script to monitor a [MiniBolt custom node](https://v2.minibolt.info/home/readme) health and activity at a glance.

## Installation
 ```sh
  $ sudo apt install jq net-tools netcat
  $ cd /tmp/
  $ git clone https://github.com/d6n13l0l1v3r/minibolt-pulse 
  $ cd /tmp/minibolt_pulse/
  $ vi *.sh  # Inspect the scripts to make sure it does not do bad things. Exit with :wq
  $ sudo chmod +x *.sh  # Install the script and make it executable
  $ sudo cp *.sh /usr/local/bin/
  ```


